Package: IfamazonratingsReliable
Type: Package
Title: Detecting the fake Amazon rating based on buyer's reviews
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("QA", "Nguyen", email = "anhmilan@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Nguyen QA <anhmilan@gmail.com>
Description: This packge is used to check if average Amazon rating of each product is reliable. 
    Reviews from buyers will be sentimental analysed using library "bing" by Bing Liu. 
    If the number of negative words is greater than 40% of total sentimental words, the product got a BAD reviews and vice sera.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0),dplyr
Imports: rvest, tidytext, tidyverse,gsubfn

